Installation

Method 1: FAP File (Recommended)

1. Download spy_camera_detector.fap from Releases
2. Copy to apps/Tools/ on your Flipper Zero SD card
3. Launch via: Applications → Tools → Spy Camera Detector

Method 2: Source Compilation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/WireBoot/flipper-zero-spy-camera-detector.git

# Build using Flipper Build Tool
./fbt fap_spy_camera_detector
```
